title: Improve Your Stock
author: Sami Meadad Choudhury
description: Ovulation induction medications, (fertility drugs), are given to stimulate the follicles in the ovaries, which will result in the production of multiple eggs in a cycle. The medications will help in controlling the time that you release the eggs, ovulating, timely sexual intercourse, intrauterine inseminations and in vitro fertilization procedures can be scheduled at the most likely time to achieve pregnancy.
